					<h2>Hi, my name is Jeith!</h2>
					<span>I'm a full stack software developer from Houston, TX. I've been coding for over 3 years, and I'm most proficent in web development. I first started learning how to code on my own through <a rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.theodinproject.com/" target="_blank">The Odin Project</a> and <a rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.freecodecamp.org/" target="_blank">FreeCodeCamp</a> and started with the basics of HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Python early 2018. Six months later, I attended <a rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.digitalcrafts.com/" target="_blank">DigitalCrafts</a> where I learned <a rel="noreferrer" href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank">Node.js</a>, <a rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.postgresql.org/" target="_blank">PostgreSQL</a>, and <a rel="noreferrer" href="https://reactjs.org/" target="_blank">React</a>. Since attending coding bootcamp, I've been working professionally as a software engineer at a startup were I build and deploy web and mobile applications using MERN-stack and various other technologies.</span>
